data.description:
The split floor plan ensures privacy for the primary suite while offering convenient access to living and entertainment spaces. Featuring a 2006 metal roof and equipped with high-efficiency solar panels, this home promises durability and significant energy savings. Adding to the home's self-sufficiency is a Generac whole-house generator, ensuring uninterrupted power and peace of mind, especially during unforeseen outages, thereby enhancing reliability and sustainability.Stepping into the fenced backyard, you will find a delightful blank canvas to design your own outdoor haven. entertainment center, or even a guest room, this space adds immense value to the property. For those preferring secure vehicle storage or workshop space, fear not! This room can be seamlessly converted back to a garage to fit your requirements.

Don't miss out on the chance to make this your forever home. Schedule a viewing today!
